txt.en: If you would like to skip the remainder of the introductory tutorial experience and be transported to Little Delving in the Shire following the burning of the town of Archet, speak with Bounder Boffin.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This quest must be completed before the tutorial is complete.</rgb>

If you choose to skip the introductory tutorial experience, you will be transported to Little Delving in the Shire after the town of Archet has been burned and will be unable to travel to Archet prior to those events.\n\nAre you sure you want to continue?
Talk to Bounder Boffin to skip the Introduction

If you would like to skip the remainder of the introductory tutorial experience and be transported to Little Delving in the Shire following the burning of the town of Archet, speak with Bounder Boffin.
<rgb=#FF0000>This quest must be completed before the tutorial is complete</rgb>
